<body>
   <p> The <b>:first-child</b> CSS pseudo-class represents the first element among a group of sibling elements. </p>
   
   <h3> Example: </h3>
   <div>
      <p> I love Codeliber and I am selected! </p>
      <p> I love Codeliber and I am NOT selected! </p>
   </div>
</body>
